{"tid":221795,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[死老坑系列]酒樓爭位打架 茶客遭茶壼車頭浴血","createTime":"2017-04-29T03:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T04:28:38.000Z","uid":122,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67f29be2618d4ef6c5196ba29dea537bce5fd6d1","tid":221795,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T03:49:30.000Z","msg":"<strong>酒樓爭位打架 茶客遭茶壼車頭浴血</strong><br />\n<br />\n即時突發 <br />\n<br />\n2017-04-29 08:24:09 HKT<br />\n<br />\n早上6時許，葵涌新葵芳花園好爵中心一間酒樓，有茶客因為爭位起衝突。83歲姓蔡老婦到來飲茶，但見平日慣常坐的座位被另一名姓郭(69歲)男子用袋霸佔。與老婦相熟的麥姓(68歲)男茶客於是代為出頭，着郭拿開袋子讓座。<br />\n<br />\n不料郭拒絕，更爆粗辱罵麥。麥登時情緒激動，「當堂發火」，涉嫌用茶壼飛掟對方，繼而互相推撞扭作一團，混亂中蔡婆婆倒地跌傷頭。職員見狀連忙報警，警方到場時，被茶壼掟中的郭頭破血流，茶壼碎片和茶葉散落地上，桌布染血，一片混亂。救護員替他包紮，連同蔡婆婆相繼送院。警方經調查後，郭和麥同涉打架，雙雙被捕。"},{"pid":"63e6acb8543c179f88026575e63352c796a70abe","tid":221795,"uid":112494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T03:50:47.000Z","msg":"快啲立法酒樓設關愛座啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b26f31daca45d316e688e2c74ae8b366734a10","tid":221795,"uid":815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T03:52:00.000Z","msg":"68歲都仲要做狗公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e2f8a5f6b88426b388b6874d5fa1a032189b05","tid":221795,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T03:53:03.000Z","msg":"刻左名咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e0d9e1f91819772b4fae0dfca1151cd275e496","tid":221795,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T03:54:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>68歲都仲要做狗公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/